      *
     C           KKEY      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           CFHIN1
     C                     KFLD           CFHIN2
     C                     KFLD           CFHIN3
     C           K#FAA     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           CBSHN1
     C                     KFLD           CBSHN2
     C                     KFLD           CBSHN3
